INSERT INTO projects (
                organization_id,
                github_repository_id,
                owner,
                name
            )
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4)
            RETURNING
                id AS "id!",
                organization_id AS "organization_id!",
                github_repository_id AS "github_repository_id!",
                owner AS "owner!",
                name AS "name!",
                created_at AS "created_at!"
